<p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">四月，春风送暖，草木蔓发。校园里，郁金香亭亭玉立，花瓣如彩绸般明艳；樱花如云似霞，微风拂过，落英缤纷。这般烂漫的春日盛景，正是踏青赏花的好时节。&nbsp;4月1日，全院师生一同进行春日赏花活动，师生们漫步花海，感受自然的蓬勃生机。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543711141.jpg" alt="1775543711141.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543711141.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543729858.jpg" alt="1775543729858.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543729858.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543743932.jpg" alt="1775543743932.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543743932.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543758995.jpg" alt="1775543758995.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543758995.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543771822.jpg" alt="1775543771822.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543771822.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543785255.jpg" alt="1775543785255.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543785255.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543797712.jpg" alt="1775543797712.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543797712.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543831408.jpg" alt="1775543831408.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543831408.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543853815.jpg" alt="1775543853815.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543853815.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543868345.jpg" alt="1775543868345.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543868345.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543890158.jpg" alt="1775543890158.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543890158.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543905359.jpg" alt="1775543905359.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543905359.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543919062.jpg" alt="1775543919062.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543919062.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543931089.jpg" alt="1775543931089.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543931089.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543945287.jpg" alt="1775543945287.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543945287.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543967079.jpg" alt="1775543967079.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543967079.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543981724.jpg" alt="1775543981724.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543981724.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543997255.jpg" alt="1775543997255.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775543997255.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775544009768.jpg" alt="1775544009768.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775544009768.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775544021365.jpg" alt="1775544021365.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1775544021365.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">在这花香弥漫的时光里，我们领略自然之美，展现青春风采，收获真挚情谊。愿这份美好常驻心间，激励我们在未来的学习生活中，如花朵般尽情绽放，向着阳光，蓬勃生长！</span></p><p><br></p>